="d5b8aa07-c686-4ec4-ad83-03323679a996" class="r-frl1uj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>•</p></span></div><div data-rid="662964a4-1839-4263-9ad8-6014b07e2a6c" class="r-1a1rpe4 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Last updated: May 21, 2025</p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="5551f95f-b425-403e-8d3d-6722c5b7f929" class="r-bnit1e"><div data-rid="0f37a735-a889-4b14-ab50-517a80d3de7c" class="r-1t02l1d alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">After 20+ Years of Smoking, I Thought the Damage Was Already Done… Then I Tried This 2-Minute Lung Detox</span></p></span></div><div data-rid="f0530c07-713b-4c6e-9d34-d8b3204409e4" class="r-19b4w4x"><div data-rid="101323eb-e43d-4c3b-9fe1-f81e8be5b747" class="r-1kk7b4f alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Words by

</p></span></div><div data-rid="01d5d327-8691-48c3-a84f-65711caa2d1b" class="r-xtb9sx alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Robert M.</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="0cc71aaa-f7bd-44de-9f49-f79ab1df4afc" class="r-1un28vy"><div data-rid="008ec248-a971-4186-9b2a-83ffb7fee09a" class="r-ereyqp"><div data-rid="23da3ea5-d0cb-4e15-8f12-04273cf7be15" class="r-k10hfu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Share</p></span></div><div data-rid="5aa30d0a-dc15-4bf0-9ab2-6b4f1f498d86" class="r-1975z2z"><picture data-rid="4452f2cc-de4b-475c-83a4-4de8e28d27aa" class="r-q1wuq9"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0771/0860/9337/files/6303b61b31a901d3ca775f52_24_facebook_dark.png?v=1739690470&amp;width=50" class="r-1belu1p" loading="eager"/></picture><picture data-rid="b14439c7-af71-4c67-8906-c49f2bafe0f8" class="r-oo4jbm"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0771/0860/9337/files/64f0a9061ca8751520c204cb_24_X_dark.png?v=1739690470&amp;width=50" class="r-jcrlci" loading="eager"/></picture><picture data-rid="10378201-47d8-48eb-ad9a-6cf409ad7c46" class="r-1urw42u"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0771/0860/9337/files/6303b62ef2e9f61c146484ed_24_pinterest_dark.png?v=1739690470&amp;width=50" class="r-14e6jly" loading="eager"/></picture></div></div><div data-rid="dd596308-7a14-4c9f-ab87-3f9f951b3149" class="r-ycdn62 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Published on: May 15, 2025</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="8b05a905-5e5d-407f-86ea-0a41940d278b" class="r-tp45iu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>I Went From Coughing My Mornings Away To Breathing Easy Enough To Play Ball With My Grandson Again.</p></span></div><picture data-rid="7e283e33-e9ec-4d60-8074-9c40f1198784" class="r-lqpzl9"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/3f7bc8cf-6d00-4d1b-83a3-c052b2c210db?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/104dc757-a446-4b8c-acc3-b99d5bc6ef22?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/104dc757-a446-4b8c-acc3-b99d5bc6ef22?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/104dc757-a446-4b8c-acc3-b99d5bc6ef22" class="r-a39oac" loading="eager"/></picture><picture data-rid="5fa2c3c6-816a-42ef-86eb-9bcedf2f4b4c" class="r-mhr7se"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/3f7bc8cf-6d00-4d1b-83a3-c052b2c210db?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/3f7bc8cf-6d00-4d1b-83a3-c052b2c210db?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/3f7bc8cf-6d00-4d1b-83a3-c052b2c210db?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/3f7bc8cf-6d00-4d1b-83a3-c052b2c210db" class="r-ryhn8t" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="3aa6ea6c-db33-44c4-b236-81b819d81f3e" class="r-lt4m7h alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>The clock read 4:12 AM as I sat on the edge of my bed, coughing into my hands again.</p><p><br></p><p>After over twenty years of smoking, I figured the damage was done and there was nothing I could do.</p><p><br></p><p>But that morning, I caved.</p><p><br></p><p>My daughter had been going on about some lung supplement that was all over her TikTok.</p><p><br></p><p>"It's just two droppers, Dad," she'd said. "People are saying it actually works."</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Thirty days later, I was running around the backyard with my grandson.</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Here's what happened—and why every smoker needs to know about this.</p></span></div><picture data-rid="6cfc7179-32f8-4d80-bf89-c22b3595b222" class="r-27h0ro"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/f118d3f6-6922-45dd-b0cf-ed5f538ae5f6?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/a131b919-97d3-4e50-9d6a-600cdc97129c?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/a131b919-97d3-4e50-9d6a-600cdc97129c?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/a131b919-97d3-4e50-9d6a-600cdc97129c" alt="Man holding chest, leaning on stair railing." class="r-8mwgfv" loading="eager"/></picture><picture data-rid="bdf70136-b724-4e6e-bfe4-3e08cc963a5e" class="r-a6r2j6"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/a131b919-97d3-4e50-9d6a-600cdc97129c?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/f118d3f6-6922-45dd-b0cf-ed5f538ae5f6?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/f118d3f6-6922-45dd-b0cf-ed5f538ae5f6?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/f118d3f6-6922-45dd-b0cf-ed5f538ae5f6" class="r-1ebikfc" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="6412ad29-b118-42e6-b654-efff02060b3d" class="r-1sqvp9v alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Every Morning Was the Same Miserable Routine</p></span></div><div data-rid="56521e12-1f17-48d2-b784-5ccb1c34b082" class="r-1ru7p2p alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>I'd wake up hacking. Then I'd walk to the kitchen short of breath. When I tried to climb the stairs, I'd end up leaning on the railing halfway up.</p><p><br></p><p>At first, I thought maybe I just needed more exercise. But no amount of "getting in shape" helped.</p><p><br></p><p>I tried everything you can think of. Humidifiers, vitamin packs, herbal teas that tasted like mud, even those overpriced "lung detox" powders I saw on social media.</p><p><br></p><p>Nothing worked.</p><p><br></p><p>Every night I'd fall asleep exhausted, only to wake up the next morning with my chest heavy again.</p><p><br></p><p>I could literally feel the buildup in my lungs - the sticky congestion that just wouldn't leave.</p><p><br></p><p>It wasn't just the coughing that bothered me. It was the fear that came along with it.</p><p><br></p><p>The thought that maybe I'd finally done it. Maybe I'd smoked myself into this being my “new normal”.</p></span></div><picture data-rid="7bc85c38-1dc0-49b8-b7e9-028a8d0ea009" class="r-1umwfrp"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/74ad214d-7057-4d5a-be9b-63b5eb7b0035?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/e7930423-b0d0-4f1c-a8a6-a75982163880?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/e7930423-b0d0-4f1c-a8a6-a75982163880?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/e7930423-b0d0-4f1c-a8a6-a75982163880" alt="Two people looking at a phone in a kitchen, with a window view." class="r-sslf7x" loading="eager"/></picture><picture data-rid="067d13b8-ac91-470f-a5fd-9cf9b52ffc26" class="r-1caw1fi"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/e7930423-b0d0-4f1c-a8a6-a75982163880?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/74ad214d-7057-4d5a-be9b-63b5eb7b0035?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/74ad214d-7057-4d5a-be9b-63b5eb7b0035?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/74ad214d-7057-4d5a-be9b-63b5eb7b0035" class="r-uysgu9" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="6e35f712-9f00-4c34-bf33-1039e78693d9" class="r-1ezfpm7 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>"You Don't Have to Live Like This Forever."</p></span></div><div data-rid="fc74479c-782c-4036-a5eb-c55100080684" class="r-10odct9 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>That's what my daughter said when I complained about how winded I felt walking to the mailbox one afternoon.</p><p><br></p><p>She told me about something she'd been seeing all over TikTok. Apparently thousands of people were talking about these herbs called Mullein and Chlorophyll that were helping them clear out years of mucus and finally breathe again.</p><p><br></p><p>She sent me a link to a company called <a href="https://www.trybetterbrand.com/products/betterlungs-r-mullein-leaf-extract"><span style="color: #2290D7FF"><u>Betterbrand</u></span></a>.</p><p><br></p><p>At first, I laughed. "Another online miracle cure," I said to her sarcastically.</p><p><br></p><p>But sitting there coughing my lungs out, I figured why not?</p><p><br></p><p>I decided to give it a try.</p></span></div><picture data-rid="397e678e-8813-4e5f-8a79-9a802643cd5e" class="r-9yi4zn"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/a65a7b83-2635-426c-97b1-dd2c0acb835f?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/7aa7572c-4710-4c78-9e2f-f63a05ffecc0?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/7aa7572c-4710-4c78-9e2f-f63a05ffecc0?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/7aa7572c-4710-4c78-9e2f-f63a05ffecc0" alt="Hand holding a bottle labeled &#x27;Better Lungs Mullein + Chlorophyll&#x27; dietary supplement." class="r-yb0c2f" loading="eager"/></picture><picture data-rid="5af9ae72-6c3a-4b75-82be-e4a129531e7c" class="r-1oknbwm"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/7aa7572c-4710-4c78-9e2f-f63a05ffecc0?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/a65a7b83-2635-426c-97b1-dd2c0acb835f?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/a65a7b83-2635-426c-97b1-dd2c0acb835f?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/a65a7b83-2635-426c-97b1-dd2c0acb835f" class="r-1t28lhm" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="6655e516-5145-4051-a274-fe50d5b4a7b2" class="r-10xnwwx alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What Happened When I Actually Tried It</p></span></div><div data-rid="17de6c67-45cd-420d-a801-e0cc886a1dbb" class="r-1w33u57 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>A few days later, the small brown bottle showed up in the mail.</p><p><br></p><p>The instructions were simple: Take two droppers under your tongue or mix with water.</p><p><br></p><p>So I did.</p><p><br></p><p>I filled a glass, added the drops, and took a sip.</p><p><br></p><p>Here's what happened over the next 30 days:</p></span></div><div data-rid="d98a5351-e049-4ac1-a6bc-95d07d918d79" class="r-c4jw6e"><div data-rid="15da2fca-425e-445a-b367-fd6e3987ae4d" class="r-igvr5p"><div data-rid="82f8290b-e1fb-4270-9fdd-20e4be521139" class="r-1cibsps"><div data-rid="80a6538d-fbd1-4d1e-afd6-4d5c8c24dc05" class="r-6d9cuf alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Day 1</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="60e17370-856b-4a0e-9512-0dca423f433d" class="r-r3w5as alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Within 24 hours of my first dose, I felt something shift. It wasn't a miracle, but it felt like my chest was opening up. I started coughing, but these weren't the dry, painful hacks that I was used to. These were real, productive coughs. For the first time in years, it felt like my lungs were actually clearing themselves out.</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="be96dfaf-265e-468e-a011-c5fa0d10f170" class="r-s4qb99"><div data-rid="37065fb5-1caf-4c87-ae75-7d1c4b718e6e" class="r-1b150zs"><div data-rid="bbae65ee-3211-4480-bc0a-11839ff0deab" class="r-11ajexh alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Day 7</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="429fef05-f775-4cda-8f09-77fe2623b394" class="r-q5n288 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>One week in and I couldn't believe the difference. I was sleeping through the night without coughing fits. No more waking up gasping for air. My morning routine went from 20 minutes of hacking to just a few productive coughs. My chest felt lighter than it had in years.</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="e052b475-111f-4f04-853f-2b033f54b36f" class="r-1bk83ex"><div data-rid="a1634e0d-e11b-427b-a881-42befadd50a4" class="r-avm8a4"><div data-rid="22a35554-ec20-4311-b549-e518d2b56194" class="r-1cr9kso alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Day 15</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="6536191c-a140-4da6-b4bf-01eae3e767e5" class="r-1pd69s9 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Two weeks and I realized I hadn't had a single dry coughing fit in days. My energy was coming back. I walked up the stairs at work without stopping halfway to catch my breath. My wife noticed I wasn't clearing my throat constantly anymore. It felt like I was getting my old self back.</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="98e72da3-7c27-4e5a-bfd8-1f8f56a0ff1d" class="r-fonz56"><div data-rid="b351b9a8-e670-4e6d-b2ff-816e5cd6094c" class="r-qpieb4"><div data-rid="2d5ab8ef-4063-4afe-9e65-24a92e219a88" class="r-17pg5u7 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Day 30</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="0d412572-4d40-495b-bcfe-fab695bea041" class="r-g6av0e alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>After a full month, I was breathing deeper than I had in a decade. The heavy feeling in my chest was gone. I could take full, deep breaths without any restriction. And the moment that really hit me? I ran around the backyard with my grandson without stopping once to catch my breath. That's when I knew this was truly helping.</p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="af8437e3-1047-47f1-a696-25bc9072a6ee" class="r-w3hybv alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>My lungs weren't suddenly perfect. They just felt clearer - like they could actually do their job again.</p></span></div><picture data-rid="ff880212-9714-4b82-8e70-186d8b5ae795" class="r-1aqrcel"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/2b3f68bb-2f8c-4a5d-b3f8-a4a86935ce07?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/fdd338a6-73ca-4f80-8eb1-bcfb30566257?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/fdd338a6-73ca-4f80-8eb1-bcfb30566257?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/fdd338a6-73ca-4f80-8eb1-bcfb30566257" alt="Close-up of green leaves and yellow flowers with water droplets on a light green background." class="r-1hmzptc" loading="eager"/></picture><picture data-rid="2d4fafc8-d250-4693-b218-c3a31c9d27d9" class="r-z6m3r0"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/fdd338a6-73ca-4f80-8eb1-bcfb30566257?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/2b3f68bb-2f8c-4a5d-b3f8-a4a86935ce07?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/2b3f68bb-2f8c-4a5d-b3f8-a4a86935ce07?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/2b3f68bb-2f8c-4a5d-b3f8-a4a86935ce07" alt="Green plant with flowers and liquid being dropped into a glass of water." class="r-1r438sr" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="744be501-1edf-44cf-937e-70c2c86e1e93" class="r-4uoye3 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>The Science Behind This "Liquid Lung Detox" </p></span></div><div data-rid="c25715e0-5e6d-4b86-ba71-2fddd4988b77" class="r-f6vu2m alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>I wanted to understand why this worked when nothing else did, so I did some more digging.</p><p><br></p><p>Turns out, Mullein has been used for centuries to support lung health. It's known for helping the body loosen and expel mucus, soothe irritation, and calm inflamed airways.</p><p><br></p><p>And when combined with Chlorophyll, which is a natural antioxidant that helps neutralize toxins from smoke and pollution, it becomes a powerful duo that supports your lungs' natural detox process.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Think of it this way: Mullein works like a gentle brush, loosening years of tar buildup, while chlorophyll neutralizes the toxins—like how it cleans the air, but inside your lungs.</strong></p><p><br></p><p>This isn't about hacking your body or "supercharging" your lungs.</p><p><br></p><p>It's about getting back to normal. It's about letting your lungs do what they were designed to do: clear themselves and breathe naturally.</p></span></div><picture data-rid="ff297ff3-9604-49e8-8a29-74f8ff652829" class="r-wy6j5k"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/36c60748-f525-48d2-9e2e-6eec187ba52c?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/daf35090-2200-4452-8b4c-9b7081e1e678?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/daf35090-2200-4452-8b4c-9b7081e1e678?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/daf35090-2200-4452-8b4c-9b7081e1e678" alt="CitrusLabs Tested logo with a check mark in a circular design." class="r-ko5rl1" loading="eager"/></picture><picture data-rid="6df8c8b6-5a81-4f92-a3ca-879c00afeaec" class="r-uu4qxx"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/daf35090-2200-4452-8b4c-9b7081e1e678?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/36c60748-f525-48d2-9e2e-6eec187ba52c?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/36c60748-f525-48d2-9e2e-6eec187ba52c?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/36c60748-f525-48d2-9e2e-6eec187ba52c" alt="Black and white badge with text &#x27;Clinically Citruslabs Tested Study&#x27; and a checkmark." class="r-1a6xfin" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="4c179667-f140-462d-8fcb-9ed8e611f8d7" class="r-1rykvf9 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>I Had to See the Proof for Myself</p></span></div><div data-rid="9cdd484a-5278-4f41-9255-0b69a2239128" class="r-8l8i1n alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Look, I've wasted hundreds on supplements that did nothing. Lung detox teas, breathing pills, all garbage.</p><br><p>So when this actually worked, I had to know why. Was I imagining it? Placebo effect?</p><br><p>Turns out, no. Betterbrand had done something almost unheard of in the supplement world—they'd run an actual clinical trial. Triple-blind, placebo-controlled, 100 participants tested for 60 days.</p><br><p>Here's what they found:</p></span></div><div data-rid="12006274-ad19-4782-a88b-59049a379764" class="r-fq2ss"><div data-rid="0a907610-230c-4e53-9f29-4e8ddd5b373e" class="r-p3312r"><picture data-rid="2b6134d2-943a-40f9-b36b-8df7632c1d06" class="r-105e3sb"><img src="https://images.replocdn.com/images/589e026e-6798-4e21-9571-840168c97505/530d1c6f-f0c5-44dd-abc8-e387f0939141" class="r-1s3rqwo" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="0c140c4a-4d31-493f-a3c2-93145fd9a596" class="r-146nalm alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>81% reported less coughing†</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="d50a2a3f-4a06-4238-a4d4-01844c5b8fa1" class="r-ndvduv"><picture data-rid="979d42f6-a478-456a-ae51-c163d12149f8" class="r-zayqz7"><img src="https://images.replocdn.com/images/589e026e-6798-4e21-9571-840168c97505/530d1c6f-f0c5-44dd-abc8-e387f0939141" class="r-19t1rok" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="1d6f382b-fc8e-4506-b199-fb228666de94" class="r-152oarl alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>79% said their airways felt clearer†</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="acf0770c-7568-4478-9901-116a8c24ada2" class="r-1qaw7f4"><picture data-rid="345d817d-cefb-4cb9-b0d5-68087742a4ef" class="r-1edd1xa"><img src="https://images.replocdn.com/images/589e026e-6798-4e21-9571-840168c97505/530d1c6f-f0c5-44dd-abc8-e387f0939141" class="r-v6vsd0" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="91b3dcdf-59be-495a-84ae-43d6d475720a" class="r-1uzt7wu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>76% said they could breathe easier†</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="47063e33-1cd8-4799-bce3-cb2bdc349b4f" class="r-1igkdi2"><picture data-rid="47d13efb-de1e-4082-bee8-38e3d2b70329" class="r-8207el"><img src="https://images.replocdn.com/images/589e026e-6798-4e21-9571-840168c97505/530d1c6f-f0c5-44dd-abc8-e387f0939141" class="r-4kz0dm" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="0ee7efb7-07a8-4cd7-bf2c-17333dfd22aa" class="r-1sd6gfj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>8 out of 10 reported feeling less fatigue†</p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="bd5af8a9-7a13-4fe5-aa20-a84610e74089" class="r-17iweca alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>And for me, those numbers translated into something even better:</p><br><p><strong>Freedom</strong>.</p><br><p>Freedom to go for a walk without stopping halfway.</p><br><p>Freedom to laugh without choking.</p><br><p>Freedom to finally take a deep breath again.</p></span></div><picture data-rid="27384979-57fe-4652-bf2e-15e483621979" class="r-vajzf8"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0832/0096/6977/files/mulleindroppergif-ezgif.com-optimize_1.gif?v=1761514019&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/63550787-2791-49b0-8692-603240f4f1a3?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/63550787-2791-49b0-8692-603240f4f1a3?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/63550787-2791-49b0-8692-603240f4f1a3" alt="Green liquid being dropped into a glass of water." class="r-n2b6t7" loading="eager"/></picture><picture data-rid="b82ad142-6f15-4cb5-a4a3-722031f29330" class="r-1yzehwr"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/586e5d0f-f4b2-420e-a544-d9d31f9580c0?width=820" media="(max-width: 