8d-b23d-32b5a504d0d6" class="r-124aem2"><div data-rid="402f75a0-0fd1-4f36-b3ae-81e0f62df5b5" class="r-p2uzg2 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Step 1</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="a1747c6d-2483-4554-a92f-7da5dcddf757" class="r-1txz9ck alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Shake the bottle well.</p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="8da8d92f-cf7b-42a1-b43f-d813ab351611" class="r-1qyv2xs"><picture data-rid="6324d7c1-1dcf-4c7c-983c-9ee6dcfad3b3" class="r-wcg840"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/012329b5-4280-443c-aa79-61af278d3e30?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/012329b5-4280-443c-aa79-61af278d3e30?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/012329b5-4280-443c-aa79-61af278d3e30?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/012329b5-4280-443c-aa79-61af278d3e30" class="r-4eypoy" loading="lazy"/></picture><div data-rid="be44c9f8-5296-44ca-9d8f-a8a941be4854" class="r-1t5ke5p"><div data-rid="25e68dd4-ee48-4ff4-80b4-9dd5dec81dd5" class="r-39xsxs"><div data-rid="de7f1c0f-2ea2-46c8-95fd-b0c4e259e77a" class="r-5pdf6x alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Step 2</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="26614a3b-62f8-4c2b-bddd-2bca9ff3e9b5" class="r-1ai6kyn alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Take two droppers under your tongue (or in water).</p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="899245dc-0389-4ddd-a681-f4f90e6de234" class="r-1r4oqh7"><picture data-rid="11ac7637-29c5-4d28-89cf-a47cad1c64c1" class="r-1wonsop"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/2b91fc5e-bb72-47f3-a445-62c0b295f5a4?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/2b91fc5e-bb72-47f3-a445-62c0b295f5a4?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/2b91fc5e-bb72-47f3-a445-62c0b295f5a4?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/2b91fc5e-bb72-47f3-a445-62c0b295f5a4" class="r-1ntgztj" loading="lazy"/></picture><div data-rid="3a17ffa8-cd46-4fe1-bd77-d9a5f36a1c7f" class="r-1r9v3fb"><div data-rid="04431923-2f1b-48b6-9a8c-ade359b7fbfe" class="r-6jlihx"><div data-rid="968aa127-65aa-45ba-82d4-556d4e84639b" class="r-1fmndqf alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Step 3</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="c05bfd33-e5c3-4dd7-a9f6-e37d8b9ea500" class="r-1dfradv alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Breathe. Let your body handle the rest.</p></span></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="4711e5b9-05e1-43f3-a98e-bb780142ab2b" class="r-1u35a3b alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>That's it.</p><p><br></p><p>No complicated steps. No brewing teas or swallowing pills.</p><p><br></p><p>A simple morning routine that supports your lungs in doing what they're meant to do, which is keeping you breathing clean, easy, and strong.</p></span></div><picture data-rid="c8c1f1d8-1095-47ab-8b36-950206487ae8" class="r-108cfky"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/646d95f1-aa18-43fb-8a44-50c63bff1925?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/646d95f1-aa18-43fb-8a44-50c63bff1925?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/646d95f1-aa18-43fb-8a44-50c63bff1925?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/646d95f1-aa18-43fb-8a44-50c63bff1925" alt="Man in white coat stands behind product display with plants and &#x27;Better Brand&#x27; sign." class="r-11z0r6i" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="2f7fcf47-2609-4390-93ae-bd5e87d0d52d" class="r-hi2c1y alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Made in the USA and Built on Integrity</p></span></div><div data-rid="f4e94541-3670-4fb0-ac21-5f643c47908f" class="r-o9vx5b alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>One thing that stood out to me was how transparent Betterbrand is.</p><p><br></p><p>They're not some random online seller. They're a veteran-owned American company that's built its reputation on real science and real results.</p><p><br></p><p>They didn't just say their product worked. They invested in actual clinical trials to back it up.</p><p><br></p><p>That alone made me trust them even more.</p></span></div><picture data-rid="248c2631-96a0-4855-8e9c-0d1f44a37703" class="r-jvh7g6"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/d5f96305-6f14-40a2-a5f1-2cd7e5ffadcc?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/3cc37b63-bcf1-42ed-9565-79c6b89de32f?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/3cc37b63-bcf1-42ed-9565-79c6b89de32f?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/3cc37b63-bcf1-42ed-9565-79c6b89de32f" alt="Mullein leaf extract bottle with matching box, both displaying a plant illustration." class="r-z1t1bo" loading="eager"/></picture><picture data-rid="718eadba-b902-494a-9181-af3b54a0079e" class="r-1qe58wf"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/3cc37b63-bcf1-42ed-9565-79c6b89de32f?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/d5f96305-6f14-40a2-a5f1-2cd7e5ffadcc?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/d5f96305-6f14-40a2-a5f1-2cd7e5ffadcc?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/d5f96305-6f14-40a2-a5f1-2cd7e5ffadcc" class="r-vycd5o" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="71df6de8-17bc-477b-ba5f-c7d653bc0b1c" class="r-19w2r92 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>I'm Not Saying It's Magic… But It Works</p></span></div><div data-rid="6f21c7a9-f4fb-4585-84a1-51062da3b7b5" class="r-1w9ax1p alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>After about two weeks, I realized I hadn't had a single coughing fit in days. My chest felt lighter. I felt less fatigued.</p><p><br></p><p>I didn't suddenly have super lungs. Just working lungs. And honestly, that’s all I wanted.</p><p><br></p><p>Now I start every morning with two droppers. It's become as routine as brushing my teeth.</p><p><br></p><p>My wife says she can tell the difference just by how I talk. There's no more shortness of breath, no more rasp in my voice.</p><p><br></p><p>And last week, for the first time in years, I ran around the backyard with my grandson without stopping to catch my breath.</p></span></div><div data-rid="1cb75f1d-830d-46cc-b653-f713d433bb48" class="r-1jj543i alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>I'm Not Alone - What Others are Saying About Mullein Tincture</p></span></div><div data-rid="7d66a1e9-a3f9-4a98-a6a7-4f0042c8b7e4" class="r-1dlz2hu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>If you look up Betterbrand's website, you'll see thousands of stories just like mine.</p></span></div><div data-rid="54174bfe-47a2-4bbc-8d86-92986a02ef66" clas